        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2019_R1_physics/q06.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "半径为 $2R$ 处的重力加速度是地表的 $1/4$，它提供向心加速度。",
        "analysis": "令角速度为 $\\omega$，有 $2R\\omega^2=g/4$。",
        "steps": [
          {
