          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑥ $4\\pi\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2R}{g}}$",
        "correctOption": "⑥"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2019-r1-phys-7",
      "number": "II-A 问1",
      "topic": "液体与金属球的热平衡",
      "topicTag": "热力学·热量守恒",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "断热容器中有温度 $t_1$ 的液体，放入温度 $t_2(<t_1)$ 的金属球，最终两者温度相同。液体热容量为 $C_1$，金属球热容量为 $C_2$。求从液体移动到金属球的热量。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$(C_1+C_2)(t_1-t_2)$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{(C_1^2+C_2^2)(t_1-t_2)}{C_1+C_2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{C_1C_2(t_1-t_2)}{C_1+C_2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$(C_1-C_2)(t_1-t_2)$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{(C_1^2+C_2^2)(t_1-t_2)}{C_1-C_2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{C_1C_2(t_1-t_2)}{C_1-C_2}$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "先求共同平衡温度，再求金属球吸收的热量。",
        "analysis": "热量只在液体和金属球之间移动，因此液体放热等于金属球吸热。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求平衡温度",
            "content": "$$C_1(t_1-T)=C_2(T-t_2)$$\n\n$$T=\\frac{C_1t_1+C_2t_2}{C_1+C_2}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 求移动热量",
            "content": "$$Q=C_2(T-t_2)=\\frac{C_1C_2(t_1-t_2)}{C_1+C_2}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "③ $\\dfrac{C_1C_2(t_1-t_2)}{C_1+C_2}$",
        "correctOption": "③"
      }
    },
    {
