        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$-6p_0V_0$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2019_R1_physics/q09.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "理想气体内能只由温度决定，而 $T\\propto pV$。A、B 两点的 $pV$ 相同。",
        "analysis": "内能变化为 0。气体做功等于 $p-V$ 图像下面积带符号；体积从 $3V_0$ 减小到 $V_0$，所以做功为负。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 内能变化",
            "content": "$$p_AV_A=p_0\\cdot3V_0=3p_0V_0$$\n\n$$p_BV_B=3p_0\\cdot V_0=3p_0V_0$$\n\n$$\\Delta U=0$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 求做功",
            "content": "$$W=\\frac{p_A+p_B}{2}(V_B-V_A)=\\frac{p_0+3p_0}{2}(V_0-3V_0)=-4p_0V_0$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 热力学第一定律",
            "content": "$$Q=\\Delta U+W=-4p_0V_0$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑤ $-4p_0V_0$",
        "correctOption": "⑤"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2019-r1-phys-10",
      "number": "III-A 问1",
      "topic": "向负 x 方向传播的波形变化",
      "topicTag": "波动·行波图像",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "$x$ 轴负方向传播、振动数 $0.50\\,\\mathrm{Hz}$ 的正弦波。图给出 $t=0$ 时的 $y-x$ 图像，判断 $t=3.5\\,\\mathrm{s}$ 时的波形。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "图①"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "图②"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "图③"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "图④"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2019_R1_physics/q10.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "频率为 $0.50\\,\\mathrm{Hz}$，周期为 $2.0\\,\\mathrm{s}$。$3.5\\,\\mathrm{s}$ 相当于 $1.75$ 个周期。",
        "analysis": "波向负 $x$ 方向传播，经过 $3.5\\,\\mathrm{s}$ 后图像向左移动 $3/4$ 个波长。此时原点处成为波谷，对应图①。",
        "steps": [
