        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac23e$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$e$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "设 u、d 的电荷分别为 $u,d$，用质子和中子的总电荷列方程。",
        "analysis": "质子 $uud$：$2u+d=e$；中子 $udd$：$u+2d=0$。",
        "steps": [
